    "description": "<p>Psions are masters of telekinesis and telepathy whose minds have ascended to be able to reach out to the world and creatures around them with their thoughts alone. They can both use telekinesis to move creatures and objects, and telepathy to assault creatures' minds.</p><p><em><strong>Source of Power</strong></em><strong>:</strong> Psions have achieved a mental state of being where they can turn their own thoughts into reality as well as reach out to the minds of others. Psions have a wide range of origin, ranging from being born with a mental connection to the world around them, a strange psychic interaction, or years of training and mental strain.</p><p> </p><h2>Starting Equipment</h2><ul><li>1 Light Weapon</li><li>1 set of Novice Light Armor</li><li>X or Y “Packs” (Adventuring Packs Coming Soon)</li></ul><p> </p><h2>Psion Spellcasting Mastery</h2><p><strong>Combat Masteries:</strong> Light Weapons, Light Armor, Spellcasting.</p><p><strong>Spell List:</strong> When you learn a new Spell, you can choose any Spell from any Spell List, but only Spells with Psychic or Gravity Spell Tags, or from the following Schools of Magic: Abjuration, Divination, Enchantment, or Illusion.</p><p><strong>Alpha Note: </strong>You get access to the “Premade List” of Psychic & Enchantment. This is the only Premade List that you have to choose from until the Spell List Alpha Update. Keep in mind that you do not get ALL of the Spells on this list, since the Psion only has 2 Cantrips and 3 Spells at Level 1.</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Cantrips Known: </strong>You learn a number of Spells with the Cantrip Spell Tag as shown in the Cantrips Known column of the Class Table.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Spells Known:</strong> You learn an additional number of Spells (with or without the Cantrip Spell Tag) as shown in the Spells Known column of the Class Table.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Mana Points:</strong> You have a maximum number of Mana Points equal to your Prime. Additionally, your maximum increases by an amount as shown in the Mana Points column of the Class Table.</span></p><p> </p><h2>Class Table</h2><table style=\"border-width: 2px; border-style: solid; width: 100%;\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: center; border-width: 2px; background-color: #8499bd;\"><p><strong>Level<